{"tid":2175799,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"郭嘉銓: 已提醒同事日後取用新聞材料要注意地方","createTime":"2020-08-26T16:34:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T16:41:08.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e79ad38eb67201babab8739d1a10e159265388fa","tid":2175799,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T16:34:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1546094-20200826.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1546094-20200826.htm&d=hjP0Q4X6c9sJGZoCRXhatkt47LdDf8L2Tg6pYSR3Psk%3D&h=a7bb9e02\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1546094-20200826.htm&h=fa526108\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1546094-20200826.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n警方召開記者會交代7.21元朗站事件的調查進展，期間新界北總區刑事總部高級警司陳天柱，展示本台於7.21當晚的片段截圖，表示有人利用有關鏡頭指「警黑勾結」，製造許多誤導新聞，形容是「剪頭剪尾扭曲表達」。<br />\n<br />\n就警方引用本台新聞片段一張截圖，描述案發情況，事前未與本台新聞部溝通，新聞部向警方提出質疑，此舉會影響新聞部的公信力。<br />\n<br />\n警察公共關係科總警司郭嘉銓回覆時表示，由於準備時間趕，未及徵求港台同意便使用，煩請見諒，亦希望港台明白警方是基於公眾利益而作有關安排。<br />\n<br />\n郭嘉銓表示，鑒於港台的關注，已提醒他的同事日後取用傳媒的新聞材料要注意的地方。"},{"pid":"e7f722bc24870e7daea540e465175789cde48070","tid":2175799,"uid":284699,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T16:35:09.000Z","msg":"成年喇<br />\n趕你老母<br />\nCLS"},{"pid":"2212d576b130ccaab249cefbfe397f1a41f94617","tid":2175799,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7f722bc24870e7daea540e465175789cde48070","tid":2175799,"uid":284699,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T16:35:09.000Z","msg":"成年喇<br />\n趕你老母<br />\nCLS"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T16:35:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" cla